.TH TELL-JOKE "1" "December 2025" "tell-joke 202208171117-git" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
tell-joke \- Tell a random joke
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B tell-joke
[\fI\,OPTIONS\/\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B tell-joke
is a script that fetches and displays a random joke from joke APIs. It can retrieve jokes from various online sources for entertainment.
.PP
The script outputs a random joke to the terminal.
